                     <interp inst="t18030112-30-off163" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18030112-30-off163" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18030112-30-cd164" type="crimeDate">9th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030112-30-off163 t18030112-30-cd164"></join>, a hammock, value 2s. a mattrass, value 15s. two blankets, value 6s. a counterpane, value 3s. a pillow, value 5s. a coat, value 20s. two shirts, value 15s. a frock, value 2s. two pair of breeches, value 4s. two handkerchiefs, value 1s. 6d. two pair of shoes, value 5s. and three pair of stockings, value 6s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18030112-30-victim208" type="victimName">
                     Edward 
                     Lawson
                  <interp inst="t18030112-30-victim208" type="surname" value="Lawson"></interp>
